I"¶<p>On touchscreens, typing by swiping means that typing becomes <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/body-movement-supports-spatial-reasoning">more kinesthetic</a>. Words become strokes with a certain <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/visual-vocabulary-is-systematic">visual identity</a>, requiring a certain careful <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/body-movement-supports-spatial-reasoning">movement</a>.</p>
